Package: Morpho
Type: Package
Title: Calculations and visualisations related to Geometric Morphometrics
Version: 0.26-00
Date: 2013-07-31
Author: Stefan Schlager
Maintainer: Stefan Schlager <stefan.schlager@uniklinik-freiburg.de>
Description: A toolset for Geometric Morphometrics and mesh processing. This includes (among other stuff) mesh deformations based on reference points, permutation tests, detection of outliers, processing of sliding semi-landmarks.

SystemRequirements: trimesh_project, rayproject, ply2ascii (http://sourceforge.net/projects/morpho-rpackage/files/Auxiliaries/)
Suggests: car, lattice, ffmanova, pls, shapes
Depends: R (>= 2.14.0), rgl, parallel, foreach, Matrix, doParallel
Imports: MASS, yaImpute, colorRamps
Copyright: see COPYRIGHT for details
License: GPL-2
LazyLoad: yes
URL: http://sourceforge.net/projects/morpho-rpackage/
